headline: Raymond James Sues Deceased Advisor’s Husband Over Laptop Possession
summary: Raymond James claims the late advisor's husband used client information on the laptop to solicit them on behalf of Wealthcare Management Services, a Bloomfield Hills, Mich.-based team affiliated with LPL Financial.
